<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ف ق م:</span> <span class="c2">(الْفُقْمُ)</span> بِالصُّمِّ اللَّحْيُ وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ: <span class="c2">«مَنْ حَفِظَ مَا بَيْنَ فُقْمَيْهِ»</span> أَيْ مَا بَيْنَ لَحْيَيْهِ. وَ <span class="c2">(تَفَاقَمَ)</span> الْأَمْرُ عَظُمَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>